# protein_dna_sequence_human_readable
Human readable sequence parser for protein and DNA

This tool takes a copy-pasted input string of a DNA or amino acid sequence, and ouputs it into 10-character blocks, 6 blocks per line, to visualize the sequence in a human-readable fashion. Demo: https://rdtls.nl/bio/

```

```
